From: Jack Thomson <jackabt@amazon.com>
Date: Tue, 2 Jun 2026 16:04:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 94/94] KVM: x86: Advertise exitless userfault async page
 faults

Advertise the optional eventfd/ring fast path with a separate
capability. Kernels that support only the base KVM_ASYNC_PF path remain
distinguishable.

Document KVM_SET_APF_EVENTFD, sync the tools UAPI headers, and extend
the selftest to cover exitless notification when
KVM_CAP_ASYNC_PF_USERFAULT_EVENTFD is present.

Signed-off-by: Jack Thomson <jackabt@amazon.com>
